{"tid":2255321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美落實對台售武 總值140億","createTime":"2020-10-23T12:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T13:18:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c31259f06af401a6eab32db63b5bf630a1218d1","tid":2255321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201023/ZUTBFTNM7FA7HJ26CVK3TI4CG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201023%2FZUTBFTNM7FA7HJ26CVK3TI4CG4%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=d76d6d32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201023%2FZUTBFTNM7FA7HJ26CVK3TI4CG4%2F&h=2b75dcf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201023/ZUTBFTNM7FA7HJ26CVK3TI4CG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美落實對台售武 總值140億<br />\n<br />\n兩岸關係不斷惡化之際，美國進一步落實對台售武，三項主要軍備包括多管火箭系統、增程導彈及偵察用吊艙，總值超過18億美元（約139.5億港元），是美國總統特朗普上任4年來第8次對台軍售。北京昨批評美國損害台海和平穩定，會根據形勢作出必要反應。中國人民大學國際關係學院教授時殷弘昨表示，此舉除有可能波及武器生產商之一─美國波音在中國的市場，也將持續衝擊中美關係及兩岸局勢。未來中國是否以商用客機訂單制裁波音，值得觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HeSnDltfhx4xBqsGstttOddc7Kg=/1994x1329/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VKKPMY2XZVAGNEQWMAJ2GBNLFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHeSnDltfhx4xBqsGstttOddc7Kg%3D%2F1994x1329%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVKKPMY2XZVAGNEQWMAJ2GBNLFI.jpg&h=71f3ab5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■洛歇馬丁的高性能多管火箭系統。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強化國軍應付區域威脅<br />\n<br />\n此次售台的三種武器系統，有洛歇馬丁的高性能多管火箭系統（HIMARS），使用227毫米火箭，最大射程300公里，美國將出售11套火箭系統；波音的空對地增程型距外陸攻導彈（SLAM-ER），射程270公里，共出售135枚；還有F-16使用的偵察用吊艙，艙內有多頻譜成像儀器，供收集情報分析圖像。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防安全合作署（DSCA）已正式知會國會，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國的外交部發言人趙立堅昨在例行記者會表示，美。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國台辦及國防部同日亦批評美國對台售武。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-UVx-GkAFNis_whu9Ho_tfXneWE=/882x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RFPJJPPI4VAZNAAJCN7HSRD5FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-UVx-GkAFNis_whu9Ho_tfXneWE%3D%2F882x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRFPJJPPI4VAZNAAJCN7HSRD5FQ.jpg&h=cef77417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美軍F-16在12,000公尺高空，距離130公里外，用「MS-110」新式偵照吊艙拍攝的加州海岸照片（圖）。 互聯網"},{"pid":"c883f06248c6093686d49a20bb99b4115f09068b","tid":2255321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5792bb07dbc7d67887e9a305a5653aa3257494e","tid":2255321,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016a027321e68a6054314f4524399ed4864c750e","tid":2255321,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71f15d206ab3fdc1c703170d1b06ecd84315c02a","tid":2255321,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"即係起台灣空域已經望到福建？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2233c9cec1cb4227bef59d4e841ea080cbff2a00","tid":2255321,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016a027321e68a6054314f4524399ed4864c750e","tid":2255321,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"F35掛MS-110，咁咪隱唔到型？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f